name: This is mine
description:
Entry for the TriJam 68! Made in a little over 4hrs. Please Enjoy and post high scores in comments.

TIPS: Sometimes the browser player disables button presses. Try a refresh or full-screen! :)

Everything lovingly made by some students from Norwich University of the Arts; Becky Reeve, Chloe Gooda, Sam Russell and Zoe Lopez. :)
